 Select TASER Models 
The affordable and preferred non-lethal choice of most law enforcement agencies, private security and regular citizens













Gun-like non-lethal weapons, like the TASER devices, are often seen on Television or in the news where an officer has to subdue a person who is not complying with his verbal commands to stop and desist. The subject is often seen posing a threat to him or herself, or others, and has to be incapacitated for the safety of the officers or of others in the vicinity. TASER handheld weapons have been shown to be extremely effective in taking down even the most aggressive person.
 
Each ADVANCED TASER® gun model uses a replaceable cartridge unit, which employs compressed nitrogen to fire two barbed probes at 160 feet per second. These probes are connected to the weapon by high-voltage insulated wire. When the probes make contact with the target, the ADVANCED AIR TASER handgun transmits powerful electrical pulses along the wires and into the body of the target through up to two inches of clothing.











